INSERT INTO `bbnposts` VALUES (1,1,'2012-11-05 02:34:47','2012-11-05 02:34:47','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2012-11-05 02:34:47','2012-11-05 02:34:47','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2012-11-05 02:34:47','2012-11-05 02:34:47','<img class=\"size-full wp-image-39 alignleft\" title=\"img-homepage-kids\" src=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/img-homepage-kids.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" />Bumble Bees Nannies is Toronto’s premier boutique nanny agency. Located in the heard of vibrant Leslieville, Bumble Bees Nannies specializes in placing the right childcare professional in the right home - from qualified Nannies, Nanny-Shares and experienced After-School Caregivers, Richelle can help you find the right solution for your family. All caregivers will have an Early Childhood qualification and/or many years experience, background and reference checks, and current CPR and First Aid certifications.\r\n\r\n“Hi, my name is Richelle and I am here to help nannies an families find each other. I hope to help families find their perfect nanny efficiently and easily, while helping nannies find a family that they love working for. In my professional career, families have told me the difficulties they faced finding a trustworthy and responsible nanny, a nanny that shared their philosophy on childcare. While caring for your children, a nanny also shares your home - it’s imperative that you are able to trust and partner with your nanny in keeing your children safe and secure. My goal in operating Bumble Bees Nannies is to find that perfect relationship for family and nanny.”\r\n\r\n- <strong>Richelle Assenberg</strong>, owner of <strong>Bumble Bees Nannies</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2012-11-07 03:15:41','2012-11-07 03: